data.description: Welcoming move in ready one of a kind jewel with foyer, massive great room with beautiful fireplace, french doors to covered back porch with extended patio and the Chef's dream kitchen with ample cabinets, lazy susan, spice rack, stainless-steel appliances new LV flooring, breakfast bar and an oversized eat in area. Primary bedroom with tray ceiling walk in closet and ensuite bath, hall bath recently remodeled with new vanity and flooring.   This 3-bedroom 2 bath home has some many unique features you won't find in this price range, just under 1/2 acre wooded lot with firepit and 300" projector screen.  No HOA!  Don't let this one slip away
